<div class="igColumns section">

    <div class="cols col-124 ">
        <div class="col col1 parsys">

                    
                        
                            <div class="hero-panel black light-text-theme"
                                 style="background-image: url('//a.c-dn.net/c/content/dam/publicsites/1511789439444/igcom/uk/images/heropanel/IG-How-to-trade-options-hero.png');">
                                <div class="fluid-width light">
                                    <h1 class="heading">如何交易期权</h1>
                                    <div class="hero-parsys parsys"><div class="igColumns section">








<div class="cols-bg 
                    
                    bg-none
                    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                    "
                    
                    >

        <div class="cols col-88">

        <div class="col col1 parsys"><div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            bg-none 
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            content-no-padding
            text-position-top
            text-no-image
            imagesize50
            
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        <div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
    
        
    



                





        <p class="primary-standfirst"><font color="white">了解期权交易的全部入门知识：包括可供交易的市场，影响期权价格的因素，以及如何开始交易期权。</font></p>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>

</div>


        
            <div class="col col2 parsys">
</div>

        

        

        
    </div>
</div>

</div>

</div>

                                </div>
                                







                            </div>
                        
                        
                    


            <div class="content-parsys parsys"><div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            text-no-image
            imagesize50
            content-margin-bot
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        <div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
    
        
    



                





        <p>不论您是在许多不同的市场中交易、对冲您现有的仓位，或者仅仅是为了拥有更多时间考虑一项交易是否适合您，<a href="/zh/options-trading">期权交易</a>都可以为交易者带来许多好处。想要开始期权交易，您只遵循需要以下几步：</p>

<ol>
	<li><a href="#prices">了解影响期权价格的因素</a></li>
	<li><a href="#risks">理解其中包含的风险</a></li>
	<li><a href="#strategy">选择一种期权交易策略</a></li>
	<li><a href="#ways">决定您想如何交易期权</a></li>
	<li><a href="#getstarted">开设您的期权账户</a>&nbsp;</li>
</ol>

<p>详细了解以上五个步骤。</p>

                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            text-no-image
            imagesize50
            
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        <div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
        <h2
            class="heading h2"
            
                id="prices"
            
        >
             什么决定了期权的价格？

        </h2>
    
    



                





        <p>期权的价格，也就是持权人支付给立权人购买期权的溢价。这个价格会根据不同的因素而产生变化。其中最大的三个因素为： 相比于执行价的<strong>标的市场价位</strong>，<strong>期权到期时间</strong>，以及<strong>标的市场波动率</strong>。</p>

<p>这些因素都遵循着一条原则： 当期权对应的标的资产价格越可能高于（看涨期权）或低于（看跌期权）其执行价格，其溢价也就越高。</p>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-right
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            
            imagesize10
            
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        
            <div class="image text-image">
                









    
    <span data-link="" data-classnames="" data-alt="" class="lazyload adaptive-image">
        
        
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1831360442.adaptive.320.medium.png/1516869215837.png"  data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 1px)"></span>
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1831360442.adaptive.320.high.png/1516869215837.png"    data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 320px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1831360442.adaptive.480.high.png/1516869215837.png"    data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 321px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1831360442.adaptive.476.high.png/1516869215837.png"    data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 481px)"></span>   
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1831360442.adaptive.620.high.png/1516869215837.png"    data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 769px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1831360442.adaptive.full.high.png/1516869215837.png"   data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 1025px)"></span> 
        
            
           <noscript>
               
                   <img src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1831360442.adaptive.320.low.png/1516869215837.png" alt="">
                   
           </noscript>
    </span>

            </div><div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
        <h3
            class="heading h2"
            
        >
             标的市场价位

        </h3>
    
    



                





        <p>当标的市场价格越接近期权的执行价格时，达到执行价格并继续超过的可能性就越高。因此，当一个<a href="/zh/forex/markets-forex/eur-usd" class="insight-link">欧元/美元</a>期权的执行价格与市场水平相差50点时，相比起另一个相差15点的期权，这个期权盈利的可能性较小，相应所要支付的溢价也较低。</p>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-right
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            
            imagesize10
            
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        
            <div class="image text-image">
                









    
    <span data-link="" data-classnames="" data-alt="" class="lazyload adaptive-image">
        
        
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1696396815.adaptive.320.medium.png/1516869345307.png"  data-width="174" data-height="164" data-media="(min-width: 1px)"></span>
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1696396815.adaptive.320.high.png/1516869345307.png"    data-width="174" data-height="164" data-media="(min-width: 320px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1696396815.adaptive.480.high.png/1516869345307.png"    data-width="174" data-height="164" data-media="(min-width: 321px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1696396815.adaptive.476.high.png/1516869345307.png"    data-width="174" data-height="164" data-media="(min-width: 481px)"></span>   
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1696396815.adaptive.620.high.png/1516869345307.png"    data-width="174" data-height="164" data-media="(min-width: 769px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1696396815.adaptive.full.high.png/1516869345307.png"   data-width="174" data-height="164" data-media="(min-width: 1025px)"></span> 
        
            
           <noscript>
               
                   <img src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_1696396815.adaptive.320.low.png/1516869345307.png" alt="">
                   
           </noscript>
    </span>

            </div><div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
        <h3
            class="heading h2"
            
        >
             期权到期时间

        </h3>
    
    



                





        <p>期权距离到期日期的时间越长，标的市场可能到达执行价格的时间也就越多。因此，当您在同一个标的市场中拥有两个相同执行价的<a href="content/igcom/zh_CN/market-training/glossary-trading-terms/out-of-the-money-definition.html">价外期权</a> 的话，离到期日期更远的那一个期权的溢价会更高一些。</p>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-right
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            
            imagesize10
            content-margin-bot
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        
            <div class="image text-image">
                









    
    <span data-link="" data-classnames="" data-alt="" class="lazyload adaptive-image">
        
        
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_586587085.adaptive.320.medium.png/1516934150561.png"  data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 1px)"></span>
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_586587085.adaptive.320.high.png/1516934150561.png"    data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 320px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_586587085.adaptive.480.high.png/1516934150561.png"    data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 321px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_586587085.adaptive.476.high.png/1516934150561.png"    data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 481px)"></span>   
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_586587085.adaptive.620.high.png/1516934150561.png"    data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 769px)"></span>  
            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_586587085.adaptive.full.high.png/1516934150561.png"   data-width="174" data-height="166" data-media="(min-width: 1025px)"></span> 
        
            
           <noscript>
               
                   <img src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_586587085.adaptive.320.low.png/1516934150561.png" alt="">
                   
           </noscript>
    </span>

            </div><div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
        <h3
            class="heading h2"
            
        >
             标的市场波动率

        </h3>
    
    



                





        <p>一个期权的标的市场波动越大，它就越有可能到达其执行价格。因此，如果市场突然出现波动性上涨 ，那么期权的溢价往往也会随之上涨。</p>

                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            text-no-image
            imagesize50
            content-margin-bot
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        <div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
        <h2
            class="heading h2"
            
                id="risks"
            
        >
             什么是期权的“希腊值”？

        </h2>
    
    



                





        <div>希腊值是与交易期权相关的个人各个维度上的风险指标。了解驱使期权价格变动的因素是实现获利交易的第一步，但是为了真正理解这个市场，您还需要掌握希腊值。因为，通过了解每一个维度上的风险，您可以采取相应措施减轻它。</div>

<div>以下是每个希腊值的简单介绍：</div>

<div>&nbsp;</div>

<ul>
	<li><a href="/zh/glossary-trading-terms/delta-definition"><strong>Delta值</strong></a>&nbsp;–&nbsp;当标的市场波动一个点的时候，相应的期权价格波动的值。 Delta值是衡量标的市场变动影响期权价格的指标，也被称为“定向风险”。</li>
	<li><a href="/zh/glossary-trading-terms/gamma-definition"><strong>Gamma值</strong></a>&nbsp;–&nbsp;当标的物市场波动一个点的时候，相应的期权的Delta值波动的值。Gamma值表明，在标的物市场波动的时候，定向风险是否会增加。&nbsp;</li>
	<li><strong>Theta值</strong>&nbsp;–&nbsp;随着时间流逝，期权的价格会磨损的值，或者可以称为期权的时间损耗风险。高Theta值的期权价值（通常是短期到期的期权）会在靠近其到期日期间迅速衰退。</li>
	<li><strong>Vega值</strong>&nbsp;–&nbsp;当标的物市场的波动率发生变化时，期权价格变化的值。当市场的波动率变化1%的时候，Vega值为2的期权的价格将会变动2个点。</li>
	<li><strong>Rho值&nbsp;</strong>–当利率产生变化的时候，期权价格变动的值。Rho可以是正值或者负值，取决于当利率是上涨（正值）或者下跌（负值）。</li>
</ul>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-full-bottom
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            text-no-image
            imagesize50
            content-no-margin
            
            js_clickable 
            
            
            
            ">

        <div class="text text-content"
                     >
                






    
        <h2
            class="heading h2"
            
                id="strategy"
            
        >
             期权交易策略

        </h2>
    
    



                





        <p>您在交易中可以使用许多交易策略，包括持有看涨期权，看涨期权价差和铁蝶策略。以下是这几个基础期权策略的介绍。</p>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















<div class="content content-component">
    <div
    
            
            
            class="theme
            
            none-bg dark-text-theme
            image-layout-right
            
            
            
            text-position-top
            
            imagesize10
            content-no-margin
            
