            <span data-src="//a.c-dn.net/c/content/igcom/zh_CN/other-markets/options-trading/how-to-trade-options/_jcr_content/content-parsys/content_component_671202919.adaptive.320.medium.png/1516328328129.png"  data-width="174" data-height="164" data-media="(min-width: 1px)"></span>
